# Protoplanetary Disk Rendering for PBRT

A tool for rendering protoplanetary disks. Uses PBRT to create the renderings and python to generate the voxel grids.

![alt text](edge_on_disk.png)

# Building

```
  cd pbrt-v3
  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake ..
```

# Running

```
python create_disk.py
```

Note, there are several parameters that can be controlled by changing values in `create_disk.py`. Look at the file for more information.
